title: Sandie Shaw - Greatest Hits
description:
Do you know that Sandie Shaw was married to
Jeff Banks.   And without telling her, he 
used her money to set up his alleged 
clothing empire.   Never said a word to
her, just went right ahead and did it.   
And then he ditched her.   After having
ripped her off.  
   Our poor Sandie was reduced to working
as a waitress in a cafe in London in order 
to make ends meet.   But the girl came 
bouncing back.   Is he a cunt or what?
